room_title: Escape room "Queen of Dragon" by Escape Newport News in Newport News
room_address: 5007 Victory Blvd., Unit D-2, Yorktown, VA 23693
room_description:
The Dragon Eggs have been stolen and locked away. You must rescue the eggs before they are destroyed. 
If you do not rescue the eggs in time all is lost and the ice walkers will take over the land destroying everything we have built over the ages.
